Python prprocessing script for Ujjivan dataset

README 

git clone  https://github.com/diamondasr/ujjivan_preprocessing.git ujjivan.preprocessings
( please note underscore in path will mess up string split used to extract utterance id)

conda activate g2p 

modify top variables of download.py depending upon dataset

Please make 2 folders audios and wavs in same directory.

python3 download.py ( Its good idea to run it on tmux )


The results are kaldi compatible directory kaldi_outputs

logs are stored in logs directory



